reviewText: I used this for my first routine for facial massage. I would buy this again, very clear video.

Being an esthetician and having had many, many classes, to me it's always good to learn more!
Even if you can pick up one more technique or piece of information to improve your skills it's worth it.
I was able to get this DVD at a great price, so there wasn't very much to lose. I have been giving luxury facials at the ski resorts for years. The DVD wasn't professionally produced but was still interesting. I wish there were more videos like one.
dvd does not play well at all,do not waste your money i also did not recieve mail label to send back.
